<div id="front_poll">
<p>With <strong>Outspokes</strong> you can get feedback on your site in three easy steps:</p>
<ol>
	<li>Tell us your site</li>
	<li>Include our script</li>
	<li>Invite commenters</li>
</ol>
<p>We're currently in private alpha.  Enter your email if you'd like to be notified when we launch.</p>
<p style="color: red"><%= flash[:warning] %></p>
<% form_for @email_req do |f| %>
	<%= f.label :email, "Email:" %><br />
	<%= f.text_field :email, :value => @old_email %><br />
	<%= f.submit "Lemme know!" %>
<% end %>
</div>